g tray and paper, mandoline or sharp knife, bowl, rolling pin, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Replace honey with cherry jam for a variation.","Will serve 6 large portions if served as a starter or lunch. If part of a sharing table or eaten at the same time as the cheese course, will serve 8."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","3h","6 portions"]}